522
00:31:26,210 --> 00:31:28,380
(Your hand needs to be higher.)

523
00:31:29,880 --> 00:31:31,359
(One, two.)

524
00:31:31,360 --> 00:31:32,729
(That's right. That's it.)

525
00:31:32,730 --> 00:31:33,900
(Again.)

526
00:31:39,490 --> 00:31:40,940
Where did your brother go?

527
00:31:45,320 --> 00:31:46,660
He left.

528
00:31:47,640 --> 00:31:49,030
He needs some time

529
00:31:49,290 --> 00:31:50,590
alone.

530
00:31:50,800 --> 00:31:52,180
Aren't you leaving?

531
00:31:56,840 --> 00:31:58,310
You might not be able to leave

532
00:31:59,050 --> 00:32:00,510
if you don't leave now.

533
00:32:02,250 --> 00:32:03,620
At least I can

534
00:32:04,290 --> 00:32:05,639
replace one of the Yinshaluo people

535
00:32:05,640 --> 00:32:07,100
and prevent another death.

536
00:32:11,540 --> 00:32:14,080
Are you trying to repay your debt?
Or do you have a guilty conscience?

537
00:32:16,840 --> 00:32:17,900
Wu Xie,

538
00:32:18,800 --> 00:32:20,990
do you really think of yourself
as the savior of the world?

539
00:32:22,080 --> 00:32:23,319
