if you wish to cancel out

542
00:32:28,160 --> 00:32:29,700
your brother's mistakes.

543
00:32:32,730 --> 00:32:34,940
Don't you have any obsessions?

544
00:32:37,290 --> 00:32:38,590
I do.

545
00:32:40,600 --> 00:32:42,830
You knew that it was an obsession.

546
00:32:43,800 --> 00:32:45,620
Why are you still trying to do it?

547
00:32:47,320 --> 00:32:49,350
I just wish to bear
some responsibilities.

548
00:32:53,290 --> 00:32:54,830
Isn't it the same for you?

549
00:32:55,800 --> 00:32:57,230
All these years,

550
00:32:58,230 --> 00:33:00,760
you've been bearing all the responsibilities
on your brother's behalf.

551
00:33:05,480 --> 00:33:07,460
If you survive this time,

552
00:33:09,250 --> 00:33:11,460
you have to learn how to be
responsible for your own life.

553
00:33:16,210 --> 00:33:17,750
If you say that,

554
00:33:19,120 --> 00:33:20,660
I'll leave for real.

555
00:33:21,320 --> 00:33:22,460
Go ahead.

556
00:33:23,050 --> 00:33:24,180
See yourself off.

557
00:33:30,320 --> 00:33:31,510
Wu Xie,

558
00:33:33,120 --> 00:33:35,310
you're truly different
from other people.

559
00:33:44,250 --> 00:33:46,140
I've already decided to stay.

560
00:33:46,600 --> 00:33:48,550
